<script setup>
import axios from 'axios';
import router from "../routes/index"

const baseUrl = 'http://localhost:4000';

function getAllPaste() {
    try {
        const response = axios.get(`${baseUrl}/bins`);
        return response.data;
    } catch (error) {
        console.error('Error fetching data:', error);
        return []; // Retourner une valeur par dÃ©faut en cas d'erreur
    }
}

function goToPaste(alias) {
    router.push({ name: 'pastDetails', params: { id: alias } });
}

function goToUpdatePast(alias) {
    router.push();
}

onMounted(async () => {
    const pastes = await getAllPaste();
    console.log('Pastes:', pastes);
});

</script>
<template>

</template>
